==制作==
比利时、法国和意大利公司联合出品<ref name=screenbase>{{Cite web|url=http://screenbase.screendaily.com/films/3724-two-days-one-night-deux-jours-une-nuit|title=Two Days, One Night (Deux Jours, Une Nuit)|work=Screenbase|publisher=[[Screen_International|Screen International]]|accessdate=2014-03-10|archive-date=2019-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909205104/http://screenbase.screendaily.com/films/3724-two-days-one-night-deux-jours-une-nuit|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并获得[[Eurimages|Eurimages]]50万欧元的资助<ref>{{Cite web|last=Rosser|first=Michael|date=2013-06-26|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/dardennes-begin-two-days-shoot/5057811.article|title=Dardennes begin ''Two Days, One Night'' shoot|work=[[Screen_International|Screen Daily]]|accessdate=2014-03-10|archive-date=2019-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204111118/https://www.screendaily.com/news/dardennes-begin-two-days-shoot/5057811.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>，总预算为700万欧元。2013年6月下旬在比利时[[瑟兰|瑟兰]]取景开拍<ref name=screenbase />。

